author: Lobo_da_boss_
title: For the size only one major inaccuracy
review:
Opening;

The Lego star wars magazine mini jango fetts slave 1 is a very good build such gains high marks in the swooshability factor .

The build-

The build uses two 1×1 trans cheese sloped for the round windshield and two modified 2×2 blue plates for the base of the ship the main nose is tiled of nicely and has a great technique to make it sturdy the main issue is one that is easily involving the two 1×2 white grill tiles they just make the wings too wide but it can easily be modified .

In conclusion-

this is a set I would recommend to star wars fans and microscale build fans .
